      <title>埃博拉疫苗可将死亡率降低一半——即使是在感染后接种</title>
      <link>https://npr.org/sections/goatsandsoda/2024/02/15/1231249465/ebola-vaccine-cuts-death-rates-in-half-even-if-its-given-after-infection</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃博拉是最可怕的传染病之一，一半以上的感染者死亡。现在已经证明一种疫苗可以将死亡率降低一半。]]></description>
      <guid>https://npr.org/sections/goatsandsoda/2024/02/15/1231249465/ebola-vaccine-cuts-death-rates-in-half-even-if-its-given-after-infection</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 17:43:33 GMT</pubDate>
