    <item>
      <title>研究发现，患者通过远程医疗和邮件获得的堕胎药是安全的</title>
      <link>https://npr.org/sections/health-shots/2024/02/15/1231652715/abortion-pill-telehealth-supreme-court-safe-study-mifepristone</link>
      <description><![CDATA[该研究调查了 6,000 名在网上预约后获得堕胎药的患者。研究发现，99.7% 的堕胎后没有发生任何严重的不良事件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://npr.org/sections/health-shots/2024/02/15/1231652715/abortion-pill-telehealth-supreme-court-safe-study-mifepristone</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 16:01:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
